[{\"slug\":\"airbrush-makeup-florida-brides\",\"title\":\"Why Airbrush Makeup Is Perfect for Florida Brides\",\"date\":\"2026-03-08T07:13:50.724Z March 8, 2026\",\"category\":\"Bridal\",\"excerpt\":\"Discover why airbrush makeup is the top choice for brides getting married in Florida's heat and humidity.\",\"content\":\"Florida's heat and humidity can be brutal on wedding day makeup, making airbrush application the smartest choice for brides. The ultra-fine mist bonds to skin and creates a weightless, sweat-resistant finish that lasts through outdoor ceremonies and outdoor receptions. At Velora Bella, our airbrush techniques are specifically designed to keep Fort Lauderdale brides looking flawless from the first look to the final dance.\"}]